OL,4,CNo apology from Boris Johnson over
OL,5,CThatcher coal mine closures remark
OL,6, Boris Johnson has declined to apologise
OL,7, amid a backlash over his remarks about
OL,8, coal mine closures under former premier
OL,9, Margaret Thatcher.
OL,11,FThe PM has faced demands to say sorry
OL,12,Fafter claiming the shutdowns in the
OL,13,F1980s gave the UK a "big early start"
OL,14,Fin fighting climate change.
OL,16,FOpposition MPs have called the comments
OL,17,Foffensive to former mining communities.
OL,19,FThe PM's spokesman said he recognises
OL,20,Fthe "huge impact and pain" of closures,
OL,21,Fbut did not offer an apology.
